sequenceDiagram
    participant U as 📱 User (WhatsApp)
    participant OC as ⚡ OpenClaw
    participant OB as 🧠 OpenBrain
    participant PF as 🔨 Plan Forge
    participant RV as Reviewer

    U->>OC: "Build user profile API..."
    OC->>OB: Query project context
    OB->>OC: Prior decisions + conventions
    OC->>PF: Launch hardening session
    PF->>PF: Generate execution contract
    PF->>U: "Plan hardened. 5 slices. Approve?"
    U->>PF: "Approved"
    
    loop Each Slice
        PF->>PF: Execute slice with guardrails
        PF->>PF: Build + Test gate ✅
        PF->>OB: Capture decisions
        PF->>U: "Slice N done. Tests pass. ✓"
    end
    
    PF->>RV: Launch review session (fresh context)
    RV->>OB: Query full decision history
    RV->>RV: Audit against contract
    RV->>U: "Review complete. 0 violations. Ship?"
    U->>RV: "Ship it"
    RV->>RV: Commit + PR
    RV->>OB: Capture postmortem
